        {
          "scid": "an6.99:1.1",
          "pli": "“So vata, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kañci saṅkhāraṃ sukhato samanupassanto … pe …",
          "en": "“Mendicants, it’s totally impossible for a mendicant who regards any condition as pleasurable to accept views that agree with the teaching. …"
        },
        {
          "scid": "an6.99:1.2",
          "pli": "sabbasaṅkhāre dukkhato samanupassanto … pe …",
          "en": "It’s totally possible for a mendicant who regards all conditions as suffering to accept views that agree with the teaching. …”"
        },
        {
          "scid": "an6.99:1.3",
          "pli": "ṭhānametaṃ vijjati”.",
